## Naming Conventions

### Variables and Functions

```typescript
// CORRECT - Uses ubiquitous language
const dailyNote = await getDailyNote(userId);
const coachReply = await generateCoachReply(message);
const hotSpots = await getHotSpots(userId);

// FORBIDDEN - Uses synonyms
const notes = await getNotes(userId);        // "notes" not in glossary
const aiResponse = await chat(message);      // "ai", "chat" not in glossary
const categories = await getCategories();    // "categories" not in glossary
```

